13 SECTION 5. IC 5-35.7-4.5 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA CODE
14 AS A NEW CHAPTER TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
15 UPON PASSAGE]:
16 Chapter 4.5. Independent Verification and Validation Oversight
17 Program
18 Sec. 1. As used in this chapter, "program" means the
19 independent verification and validation oversight program
20 established by the department under section 2 of this chapter.
21 Sec. 2. Not later than June 30, 2026, the department shall
22 establish and maintain an independent verification and validation
23 oversight program to provide independent oversight of contracting
24 activities conducted by state agencies.
25 Sec. 3. The program may review, assess, and issue required
26 changes and recommendations for contracts between state agencies
27 and contractors.
28 SECTION 6. IC 5-35.7-8 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA CODE
29 AS A NEW CHAPTER TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
30 UPON PASSAGE]:
31 Chapter 8. Procurement and Purchasing Governance
32 Sec. 1. This chapter applies to all state agencies.
33 Sec. 2. (a) Beginning July 1, 2026, each state agency shall submit
34 an annual procurement and purchasing plan to the department
35 and the budget agency.
36 (b) An annual procurement and purchasing plan required under
37 subsection (a) must include at least the following:
38 (1) All requests for procurement the state agency anticipates
39 to be solicited in the subsequent state fiscal year.
40 (2) A strategy to complete contracts scheduled to expire in the
41 subsequent state fiscal year.
42 (3) Any other information required by the department.
